   anything youâ€™re eating.  However, during my second visit I stayed at
   Khaosan Kyoto Theater, a hostel located very nearby on Gokomachi-dori.
    When I recognized it as a restaurant Iâ€™d seen on Happy Cow, I decided
   to give it a shot.  Iâ€™m SO grateful I did!

   Everything at Mumokuteki is vegan EXCEPT that some items contain fish.
    In the past these items werenâ€™t clearly labeled, which lead to some
   very unhappy vegetarians and some poor reviews on Happy Cow.  However,
   theyâ€™ve since made their menu much more clear, and now mark all
   fish-containing dishes on the menu (look for a little fish-shaped
